<title>USA: Alcoa names Alain Belda as COO, president.</title>
<headline>Alcoa names Alain Belda as COO, president.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-01-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Aluminum Co of America said it named its vice chairman, Alain Belda, president and chief operating officer of the company.</p>
<p>The company did not prvide further details.</p>
<p>Officials there were not immediately available to comment.</p>
<p>Belda, 53, will have full responsibility for all operating activities at Alcoa.</p>
<p>He joined the company in 1969 and has been vice chairman since 1995.</p>
